txt.en: Kindred to the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl

You have proven yourself invaluable to the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl. Whether or not the Kindred of the Coins deems it so, the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl now count you among their own, and your deeds are celebrated throughout the City of the Corsairs.
You must earn Kindred standing with the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl
